 SOURCE_URL_FULL=https://github.com/CISOfy/lynis/archive/$VERSION.tar.gz
      SOURCE_VFY=sha256:48d829d0dc2c583a3e838cc09a7190b69a3af844bcb913c7cf9c0226b04b95c5
        WEB_SITE=https://github.com/CISOfy/lynis/
         ENTERED=20160214
         UPDATED=20260627
           SHORT="Security and system auditing tool to harden Unix/Linux systems"

cat << EOF
Lynis is a security auditing for UNIX derivatives like Linux, Mac OS X, BSD, and
Solaris. It performs an in-depth security scan on the system itself, with the
goal to detect issues and provide tips for further system hardening. It will
also scan for general system information, vulnerable software packages, and
possible configuration issues.
EOF
